Rating: 4
This is my favorite desert recipe ever. People cant seem to get enough when i serve it. Yes - recipe makes too much custard but I like to fill pie to the top. I use a mixture of apples (i.e. Fuji,honey crisp, etc..) to keep it interesting. The combination of the custard and the fruit is irresistible.

