Rating: 4
I have made this two or three times since last fall, and it is one of my favorite pies of all time. I think the custard-apple comination is perfect and different from a simpler apple pie. So if you like custard, you will likely also like this pie. I can't speak for the crust, since I just used the recipe I am used to (and the recipe I know I like). I also like that it is a single crust pie because I'm not the greatest pie crust fan generally. I love this apple pie!

